b'800 Grand prix wins for #Honda Motorcycles!

With Honda #Moto3 rider Jaume Masia claiming victory today in the Moto3 class, in Round 12 of the 2020 FIM World Championship Grand Prix at MotorLand Arag\xc3\xb3n in Spain - Honda has now achieved an unprecedented 800 grand prix victories.

Starting way back in 1961, with a win in the 125cc class of the Spanish Grand Prix, today marks an incredible victory milestone.
